    "overall_conclusion": "No probability-based combat. All 'fights' are either (1) player choice between explicit WIN/LOSE links, (2) equipment-gated (have item = win path), or (3) puzzle-based. Combat sampling of 10+ rounds per encounter shows 0 variance — 10/10 wins on WIN link, 10/10 losses on LOSE link."
